strings: <voice_0x01001CF0><se_high>media princess: I'm very scared. Living under this sky is unbearable. very bad
<voice_0x01001CF1><se_high>media princess: Does that mean we've reached our goal?
<voice_0x01001CF2><se_high>media princess: This insult pales in comparison to the pure Predator mentality.
<voice_0x01001CF3><se_high>media princess: So the <hero> should be removed. Everyone's lives are in danger.
<voice_0x01001CF4><se_high>media princess: Do you think that if I win I'll be like this again?
<voice_0x01001CF5><se_high>media princess: Or maybe you think you want to spend the rest of your time talking?
<voice_0x01001CF6><se_high>media princess: When he calms down, he wants to travel the world with <hero>, but the curse cannot be lifted.
<voice_0x01001CF7><se_high>media princess: So it wouldn't be bad to marry such a hooligan...
<voice_0x01001CF8><se_high>media princess: I want to spend the rest of my life hugging you and taking you everywhere.
<voice_0x01001CF9><se_high>media princess: If you don't mind, take care of me, I won't leave you, I promise.
